&lt;div id=&quot;ac-128111&quot; class=&quot;c-accordion__content&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 2 years relevant professional working experience from one or more of the following:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Civil society organizatio

