&lt;h2 class=&quot;entry-title&quot;&gt;Obstetricians/Gynecologists&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;subhead&quot;&gt;MSF obstetricians/gynecologists play a crucial role in changing the lives of women worldwide, managing deliveries in remote areas and providing care for women in conflict zones.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;ac-174620&quot; class=&quot;c-accordion__content&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;ac-174621&quot; class=&quot;c-accordion__content&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;at-174621&quot; class=&quot;c-accordion__title js-accordion-controller&quot;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
