&lt;ul class=&quot;wp-block-list&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HIV, prevention of mother-to-child transmission, management of sexually transmitted infections, management of care for survivors of sexual assault&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of French or another language (Arabic, Spanish)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Course in tropical medicine and/or infectious diseases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Microsoft Office software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
