&lt;ul class=&quot;wp-block-list&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant experience in hospital settings or remote locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of other language (Arabic, Spanish, French)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Microsoft Office software (especially Excel)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
